        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-24 17:25:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n> \n> To ensure project consistency, please use the ccsdk parent pom for springboot instead of specifying your own versions.\n\nDan, CCSDK Parent Spring boot is 1.X version, CDS started with Spring boot 2.X version and CDS is not backward compatible with 1.X version or it can't be downgraded.Please suggest the next action.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "3bee05fd797c34bacba3cfd3ddc49b37306c287c",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 87,
          "name": "Dan Timoney",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "dtimoney@att.com",
          "username": "djtimoney"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-29 14:54:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> > Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n> > \n> > To ensure project consistency, please use the ccsdk parent pom for springboot instead of specifying your own versions.\n> \n> Dan, CCSDK Parent Spring boot is 1.X version, CDS started with Spring boot 2.X version and CDS is not backward compatible with 1.X version or it can't be downgraded.Please suggest the next action.\n\nThere are 2 springboot parents: one for springboot 1, and one for springboot 2.  The one you want is:\n\n<groupId>org.onap.ccsdk.parent</groupId>\n<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-parent</artifactId>\n<version>1.3.0-SNAPSHOT</version>",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
